text:
I wanted to
do communication studies for three years now. When i was younger, i
didn't know what i wanted to do but when i arrived in high school i met a
teacher that completly change my life. Before becoming a teacher, she organized
concerts all around the world and when she said this to me it was clear, i
knewn immediately that i wanted to do this job or at least something in the
world of event.She made me dream when she was talking about the countries that she visited with her job. Her memories
was my motivation to work a lot in high school to then have a good university. When i doubt of myself, i think of her. She’s my biggest inspiration. She was here when i had to sign in to university, she was concerned about my future.
The other big inspiration for me was when i went at a concert two years ago. I didn't focus on the singer at all but on the staff. I looked everyone of them and i felt that my heart was beating very fast. I knew at this moment that it was my destiny and if i wanted to my dream i must think of this moment as a motivation. When it's hard to work, i think of them and i remenber the feelings that was in my heart, it inspires me a lot to continue.
